The paper discusses the development of a Protege plugin that allows users to enter OWL axioms using rules. This involves the conversion of rules into OWL DL axioms, which is a topic that falls under the category of knowledge representation and reasoning (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of description logic (cs.LO) and the plugin being developed for Protege (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of rules in modeling OWL (cs.PL) and the conversion of rules into OWL DL axioms (cs.DL).
